Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto is over here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is not human...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sai, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.\NContinue to observe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:03:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.58,0:03:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't pierce through...\N{\i1}even with my snake sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is what Master Jiraiya\N{\i1}was referring to when he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}he's "like a small Nine-Tailed Beast."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.66,0:06:00.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(711,612)}Sakura's Tears\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not like a Ninja battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but more like\Na battle between monsters...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.82,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's useless to go on fighting\N{\i1}with the snake sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's the situation like?\N{\i1}Is Naruto dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.96,0:07:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he still wants\Nto save Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.39,0:07:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,even in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I am going to take back Sasuke,\N{\i1}no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's my lifelong promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sakura! I...will keep my promise,\N{\i1}no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To stand firm with what I say...\N{\i1}That's my Way of the Ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By now, even his self-consciousness\Nis gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What a sad kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get close to Naruto\Nin that state!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.42,0:09:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...that's enough!\NI will save Sasuke, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto, it's enough...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.89,0:09:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.31,0:11:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now is my chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's about time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As expected,\N{\i1}this body is rejecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Too bad, but the fun ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Patience... Patience now...\NI have Sasuke with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn!\N{\i1}I didn't make it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you step in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're rushing to conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't plan to fight you guys\Nanymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.97,0:13:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... it's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We both have the same goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.00,0:14:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I let you live...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you might\Njust get rid of one more Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The wounds are healing\N{\i1}much slower than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.00,0:14:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I can't stay\N{\i1}playing "volunteer" for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.22,0:15:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lord Orochimaru is also\N{\i1}reaching his limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange for helping you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,please get rid of as many\Nof the Akatsuki as you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.69,0:15:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That said, that is your teammate...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time to leave, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.96,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now's the only chance...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Danzo's man.\NI am not your enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.45,0:16:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something\Nto speak to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hokage Style: Elder Jutsu
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,10th Edict on Enlightenment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.81,0:18:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Danzo...that doddering old fool\Nis still alive, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.65,0:18:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:19:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a message from Danzo\Nto Lord Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose your words carefully\Nwhen you talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.46,0:19:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I can only relay\Nwhat Danzo has told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If that does not satisfy you,\Nthen I'll leave it up to you...
